name: No Man's Land (KCnicdao123)
description: No Man’s Land is a story about a young explorer traveling with his captain. As they stumble upon an island in the middle of the ocean, they notice that not only were they in uncharted territory, but they are in a place where no man has survived this land. Can this young explorer find a way to escape this unusual place? Will he find help among friends, or will they turn out to be his/her foes?
